CSS - BOX model : Margin Padding and Borders
Whatever we write in HTML will be a box
Every box will have content, padding, border, margin
Look at the website
By default the browser will add margin and padding and many other CSS, so reset it using the universal selctor

(imp)
total dimmension is calcuated using : website
box-sizing: border-box if this is not included then the mentioned height or width is only for the content
when its mentioned: it will include border and padding included and margin is not included
box-sizing: border-box changes the defination of height 

margin collapse (imp)
whenever two margin coincide then max margin will be be put 
